{"tid":1722464,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"嶺大宣布即時終止上學期餘下面授課堂","createTime":"2019-11-15T01:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T03:38:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3529bed465808e145cd776e2290306f14c635bfd","tid":1722464,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:55:56.000Z","msg":"嶺南大學宣布，即時終止上學期餘下面授課堂，並改為網上進行。<br />\n<br />\n嶺大表示，鑒於交通阻塞和社區衝突情況持續，以及學生對自身安全越來越擔憂，嶺南大學決定即時終止上學期餘下所有面授課堂，並改為網上進行。同學如需老師個別指導，可使用最合適的方式與他們聯繫，老師亦會使用不同方法促進學習。<br />\n<br />\n嶺大表示，期終考試將根據個別課程老師的決定，以網上考試或其他考核方式代替，同學所有考核都合格將可獲取應得學分。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492340-20191115.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492340-20191115.htm&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjQX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=ffc4775a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492340-20191115.htm&h=8249973c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492340-20191115.htm</a>"},{"pid":"20db284f587bfeb744e8dac0d26ffaf402ecf5a5","tid":1722464,"uid":171668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:07:15.000Z","msg":"學期餘下<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">的</span>面授課程"},{"pid":"58ba87ad5d1e35a6a405b1bdd213140ebc819085","tid":1722464,"uid":37600,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:08:59.000Z","msg":"大學界IE？"},{"pid":"e128e88d88ed972c3f0ea16f18db1db3eac17df0","tid":1722464,"uid":161125,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:11:06.000Z","msg":"又關你嶺南事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9acbc390c7d4f4cc3aeeb9845b951fd165ab77","tid":1722464,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58ba87ad5d1e35a6a405b1bdd213140ebc819085","tid":1722464,"uid":37600,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:08:59.00